OL,3,CFormer soldier who performed sex acts
OL,4,Con young child in the 1980s jailed
OL,6,FA former soldier from Guernsey has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed for sexually assaulting a
OL,8,Fyoung child in the 1980s.
OL,10,FDarrin Garnham, 62, was sentenced to
OL,11,F21 months in prison at Guernsey's
OL,12,FRoyal Court today for four offences
OL,13,Fwhich involved making a girl between
OL,14,Fthe age of seven and nine perform a
OL,15,Fsex act on him in a bathroom.
