OL,6,FGarnham's 21-month sentence was for
OL,7,Fone count of oral penetration while
OL,8,Fthe other three counts, which included
OL,9,Fmaking his victim touch his penis,
OL,10,Ftouching her vagina and ejaculating on
OL,11,Fher while she was lying on a sofa,
OL,12,Fcarried an 18-month sentence which
OL,13,Fwill be served as part of the total
OL,14,Fsentence.
OL,16,FGarnham was in his late teens at the
OL,17,Ftime and was on leave in the island
OL,18,Fwhile he was serving for the Royal
OL,19,FArtillery in Germany.
