OL,6,FThe victim told the court she had
OL,7,Fsuffered throughout her life as a
OL,8,Fresult of the crime and that it had
OL,9,Fcaused her to leave family and friends
OL,10,Fin the island.
OL,12,FShe added that she has "constant"
OL,13,Fflashbacks to the assault and lives in
OL,14,Ffear.
OL,16,FThe victim also said she had become an
OL,17,F"overprotective parent" out of fear
OL,18,Ffor her children succumbing to the
OL,19,Fsame kind of attack.
