OL,7,Fpolice in February last year after the
OL,8,Fvictim came forward.
OL,10,FShe had previously told healthcare
OL,11,Fadvisors and her sister about what
OL,12,Fhappened, as well as phoning Garnham
OL,13,Fto confront him, where he denied her
OL,14,Faccusations.
OL,16,FDuring the sentencing, the Judge said
OL,17,FGarnham had "taken away" the victim's
OL,18,F"safe space" through his offences,
OL,19,Fadding "you were only just an adult
OL,20,Fbut do not accept your guilt."
